view is typically used to convey information about the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotation or to link to custom information provided by your application.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the view you specify is a descendant of the "},{"code":"UIControl","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" class, you can use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the map view’s delegate to receive notifications when your control is tapped,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by implementing the "},{"code":"-mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method. If the view you specify does not descend from "},{"code":"UIControl","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", your view is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"responsible for handling any touch events within its bounds."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If this method is absent from the delegate, or if it returns "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"standard callout view has no accessory view on its right side. The return value"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of this method is ignored if "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:"},{"type":"text","text":" is present in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the delegate."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To display a view on the callout’s left side, implement the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"-mapView:leftCalloutAccessoryViewForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]},{"text":"Related examples","anchor":"Related-examples","type":"heading","level":4},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"TODO: Default callout usage, learn how to modify the view that is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"displayed on the right side of the standard callout bubble.","type":"text"}]}]}],"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:rightCalloutAccessoryViewForAnnotation:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:rightCalloutAccessoryViewForAnnotation:","roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:rightCalloutAccessoryViewForAnnotation:"}],"title":"mapView:rightCalloutAccessoryViewForAnnotation:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L963"},"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:rightcalloutaccessoryviewforannotation:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Returns the view to display on the right side of the standard callout bubble.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:rightCalloutAccessoryViewForAnnotation:":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:rightCalloutAccessoryViewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"mapView:rightCalloutAccessoryViewForAnnotation:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:rightCalloutAccessoryViewForAnnotation:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:rightCalloutAccessoryViewForAnnotation:"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns the view to display on the right side of the standard callout bubble."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:rightcalloutaccessoryviewforannotation:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","tex